%% DG-401: Authentication Sequence Diyagrami
%% Durum: DRAFT
%% Editor: https://mermaid.live
%% Aciklama: Login, register, token refresh, sosyal giris akislari
%% ---

sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Client as Frontend
    participant API as API Server
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant DB as Database
    participant Email as Email Service
    participant Google as Google OAuth

    Note over User, Google: === KAYIT AKISI ===

    User->>Client: Kayit formu doldur
    Client->>API: POST /auth/register {email, password, name}
    API->>API: Input validation (Zod/Joi)
    API->>DB: Email mevcut mu?
    DB-->>API: Mevcut degil
    API->>API: Password hash (bcrypt/argon2)
    API->>DB: INSERT users
    API->>Email: Dogrulama emaili gonder
    API-->>Client: 201 {message: "Dogrulama emaili gonderildi"}
    Client-->>User: "Email adresinizi dogrulayin"

    Note over User, Google: === LOGIN AKISI ===

    User->>Client: Email + sifre gir
    Client->>API: POST /auth/login {email, password}
    API->>DB: Kullanici bul
    DB-->>API: User record
    API->>API: Password verify
    API->>API: Generate JWT (access 15dk + refresh 7gun)
    API->>DB: Save refresh token + device info
    API-->>Client: 200 {access_token, refresh_token}
    Client->>Client: Token'i httpOnly cookie'ye kaydet

    Note over User, Google: === TOKEN REFRESH ===

    Client->>API: POST /auth/refresh {refresh_token}
    API->>DB: Refresh token gecerli mi?
    DB-->>API: Gecerli
    API->>DB: Eski token sil (rotation)
    API->>API: Yeni access + refresh token olustur
    API->>DB: Yeni refresh token kaydet
    API-->>Client: 200 {new_access_token, new_refresh_token}

    Note over User, Google: === GOOGLE LOGIN ===

    User->>Client: "Google ile Giris" tikla
    Client->>Google: OAuth redirect
    Google->>User: Onay ekrani
    User->>Google: Onay ver
    Google->>Client: Authorization code
    Client->>API: POST /auth/social {provider: "google", code}
    API->>Google: Code -> token exchange
    Google-->>API: {id_token, email, name}
    API->>DB: Email ile kullanici ara/olustur
    API-->>Client: 200 {access_token, refresh_token}
